data.title: How to Call Santo Domingo
data.meta_description: Learn how to call Santo Domingo from USA.  Find calling codes here.
data.text:
Santo Domingo is hard to miss on a map, but for former residents now living in the US, it‘s simply far too easy to miss...period.

Let‘s take a look at how to call Santo Domingo from the USA:

Start with 1 -- the country code for the Dominican Republic.

Next, enter 829 -- the Santo Domingo area code, part of the North American Numbering Plan.

Then, dial the 7-digit local phone number.

Here‘s what a call to Santo Domingo should look like:

1 + 829 + XXX-XXXX

If you don‘t know how to dial other major cities besides Santo Domingo, read up on how to call the Dominican Republic from the US to learn more!

There should be nothing left to talk about in terms of calling Santo Domingo from US, but you can read on to learn more about the capital of the Dominican Republic.
